      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is an excellent option for a buyer seeking a dependable daily driver. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and slight fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some wear and staining consistent with its age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may eventually require some routine maintenance to keep it in peak shape. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
