    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example is mechanically pristine, with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The Getrag six-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, feeding power through a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original kinematics with no bushing play, providing the razor-sharp turn-in and high-speed stability this chassis is renowned for. This is an uncompromising, turn-key machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
